Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery allows you to Define Your Target Outcome, Prepare Data for Analysis, Create and Manage Models, Explore Data Insights, Predict & Improve Outcomes, and Decision Optimization (Beta).

You can Set Up Einstein Discovery, Get Started Using Einstein Discovery, Build Models in Einstein Discovery, Open a Model, Navigate a Model, Edit Model Settings, Track Model Versions, View Model Versions, Cancel a Model Version, Compare Model Versions, Handle Quality Alerts.

Einstein Discovery models are saved with each update and you can revisit previous versions. Disparate impact is advised when recent version updates affect sensitive variables. You can add descriptions to model versions for tracking updates.
title: Viewing Model Versions in Salesforce Einstein Discovery
